descr: "The MeasureReport resource contains the results of evaluating a measure."

fields.name: value
fields.descr: "The value for this stratum, expressed as a string. When defining stratifiers on complex values, the value must be rendered such that the value for each stratum within the stratifier is unique."

fields.name: population
fields.descr: "The populations that make up the stratum, one for each type of population appropriate to the measure."

fields.name: measureScore
fields.descr: "The measure score for this stratum, calculated as appropriate for the measure type and scoring method, and based on only the members of this stratum."
